author: Marian Schoppman
title: Marian Schoppman
text: I had the best experience buying my new Toyota Corolla. My salesman, Micheal Grega was terrific. The process was fast, easy and hassle free and the price out the door was terrific. Better than any other dealership offered me. THANKS Michael.
